Utils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	makeAddressPrimary: function( addressID ){
		try{
			var answer;
			
			addressID = this.getParameter( 'sysparm_sysid' ) ? this.getParameter( 'sysparm_sysid' ) : addressID;

			gs.info('JD: Address ID: ' + addressID);
			
			var gr = new GlideRecord( 'x_602310_acct_addr_address' );
			
			gr.get( addressID );
			gr.setValue( 'primary', true );
			gr.update();
			
			answer = 'The primary address for this account has been updated.';
		}
		catch(e){
			answer = 'Error: ' + e.name + ' - ' + e.message;
		}
		
		return answer;
	},
	
    type: 'Utils'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-09-11 17:30:30</sys_created_on><sys_id>383dba5d2fa6b010a4cc2ea62799b6bd</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Utils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="demo_account_address" source="x_602310_acct_addr">e9bf6a512fa6b010a4cc2ea62799b65b</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="demo_account_address">e9bf6a512fa6b010a4cc2ea62799b65b</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_383dba5d2fa6b010a4cc2ea62799b6bd</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-09-11 18:43:12</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
